	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="goto 205 406&#xD;&#xA;oe denraiddone&#xD;&#xA;walk inside the grove to the middle of the cave&#xD;&#xA;oe snakecourtdone&#xD;&#xA;oe killgobleaders&#xD;&#xA;goto 211 456&#xD;&#xA;talk to Zevlor (he's up the ladder there)&#xD;&#xA;go to camp, after the camp intro you can see that a bunch of tieflings are there&#xD;&#xA;goto -629 -161 (that's a position in the camp, where Kagha + the parents are)&#xD;&#xA;If parents aren't visible (previous bug) use:&#xD;&#xA;setOnstage S_DEN_ParentA&#xD;&#xA;setOnstage S_DEN_ParentB&#xD;&#xA;Talk to one of the parents. Use shift+Q or roll amazing to make sure you succeed your persuasion and save Kagha. You can skip through the dialog&#xD;&#xA;Now Kagha has the dialog DEN_ShadowDruid_LeaderSaved" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
